{"tid":1592642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「梗係想搵哥哥啦邊有人想要弟弟」呢句真係難聽過粗口","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T17:16:29.000Z","uid":302314,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a8d6a04e9f6848ac1a4b5c2504b8c3d1c4d725","tid":1592642,"uid":302314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"到底我做錯咗啲咩要生存喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鐘意大過自己 或者成熟既有錯嘛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解唔鐘意自己同年齡層或者細過自己既就好似比人都歧視咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想搵人圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1144b6b689bc6968c9dd6b8f0382e79a37ac8f","tid":1592642,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"7d1991878a9fb1e0a430472a98fea46ea9defda6","tid":1592642,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a09b5a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTs8Wx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTs8Wx.jpg&h=306d0b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;關於Logo投票&gt;</span></span><br />\nHK Assembly成立的目的，不單是讓全港市民議論政事，更希望建立民主平台，讓全民以公投方式發聲，同時將平台民主制度完善，成為能與政制競爭的類政制。<br />\n但是在達到理想前，必須逐步累積技術和經驗。因此，我們決定對投票機制進行第一次測試，以現階段盡量民主的方式讓大家選出共同的「香港全民議政會」Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;投票機制&gt;</span></span><br />\n投票採用兩輪的簡單多數制。最高票數的兩款將交由設計師作最後加工，在第二輛投票獲較高票數的一款將成為 HK Assembly 的官方 Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">規則：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">一人一票</span> [1] <br />\n2. 第一輪投票時間：<span style=\"color: violet;\">24/9 11PM - 26/9 11PM</span> （香港時間，共48小時）[2]<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a09b5a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [3]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票需要你：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">加入Channel：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a09b5a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: violet;\">投票</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">叫朋友</span>加入Channel一起投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;感謝支持&gt;</span></span><br />\n集合全港多名設計精英，文宣組共設計了七款 Logo，在此先向這些有心人<span style=\"color: violet;\">致謝</span>。<br />\n希望藉著這次投票，和大家一起開始建立<span style=\"color: violet;\">真正屬於香港人的民主議政平台</span>。<br />\n隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家<span style=\"color: violet;\">投票救港</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=a09b5a3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">隨意門：《香港全民議政會》 HK Assembly 正式成立 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：<br />\n1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題<br />\n2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高<br />\n3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n4. 對此投票問題，控制投票結果的誘因不大<br />\n[2] 兩款設計交由設計師作最後加工後，第二輛投票預計於29/9進行<br />\n[3]<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】</span></span>隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"ec30f1b2fe4d3a3ecfce01f99ffd72960bcb95f9","tid":1592642,"uid":302314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf1144b6b689bc6968c9dd6b8f0382e79a37ac8f","tid":1592642,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:20.000Z","msg":"9.29 10.1 街上見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53565109dda0857537994fdfd42575fedf14777f","tid":1592642,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"錢=資源=選擇=成熟"},{"pid":"6a5740a0b3edacae659ac5d1403a74148aff2a7d","tid":1592642,"uid":302314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53565109dda0857537994fdfd42575fedf14777f","tid":1592642,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"錢=資源=選擇=成熟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hk